comments: Crowder (UTA) briefly grasps Paul's (HOU) arm on the perimeter but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
LAR shows Paul (HOU) releases from the contact with Crowder (UTA) and does not extend his arm into him and dislodge him from his defensive position.
LAR shows Paul (HOU) makes some contact with Crowder (UTA) as he secures the ball but does not dislodge him from his rebounding position.
Paul (HOU) makes incidental contact with Crowder's (UTA) foot as he secures the rebound.  Following the contact, Crowder (UTA) maintains his pivot foot on the floor before releasing the pass.
RLB shows Tucker (HOU) makes tactile contact to Rubio's (UTA) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his  shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) and O'Neale (UTA) briefly engage and disengage.
Harden (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mitchell (UTA) and briefly grasps his arm.
Gordon (HOU) initiates some contact with Gobert (UTA) with his off-arm, but does not ward off or otherwise affect his ability to contest the driving shot attempt.
Mitchell (UTA) makes contact with Capela's (HOU) shoulder and restricts his ability to jump for the rebound.
Mitchell (UTA) makes contact with Tucker's (HOU) shoulder and affects his ability to secure the ball.
O'Neale (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Gordon's (HOU) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (HOU) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gordon (HOU) makes clean contact with the ball during Mitchell's (UTA) drive to the basket.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Tucker (HOU).
Harden (HOU) cleanly dislodges the ball from Gobert (UTA) during his shot attempt at the basket.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
O'Neale (UTA) initiates body to body contact with Harden (HOU) that affects his SQBR.
Gobert (UTA) has his arm extended during the screen but Harden (HOU) is able to move through the contact.
Harden (HOU) places an arm to the front of Mitchell (UTA) during the drive but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
LAR shows Gobert (UTA) places his arms on Tucker's (HOU) shoulders, but releases and does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Crowder (UTA) commits a take foul on Paul (HOU).
Gobert (UTA) places an arm around Paul (HOU) but immediately slides it off without affecting his ability to defend the play.
Capela (HOU) briefly engages with Gobert (UTA) but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
RLB shows Capela (HOU) makes marginal contact with Gobert's (UTA) off-arm that does not affect his shot attempt near the basket.
Mitchell (UTA) briefly grasps Tucker's (HOU) arm during the rebound but does not affect his ability to get to the ball.
Capela (HOU) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
